            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮田(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7709:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7709\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7709-TW</a>)30日10:46股價上漲4.2元，報62.0元，漲幅7.27%，成交819張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮田(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7709:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7709\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7709-TW</a>)所屬產業為電機機械，主要業務為立式車床。立式車銑複合機。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲36.64%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.57%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-19 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-28 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+9 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
